CSD Python API Script Licence v2

The CCDC makes available example scripts and documentation files (the “Software”) that illustrate use of the Cambridge Structural Database (CSD) Python Application Programming Interfaces (APIs) and other CCDC software products. These scripts and modified versions may be used for any purpose and we encourage you to share these with other members of the community, subject to the following conditions:

